{"tid":1688660,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[賣港賊之一]如果連CCTVB都入唔到制裁名單 抗爭？不了","createTime":"2019-11-02T13:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T05:51:34.000Z","uid":293667,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"167a151f41f541b660071fdc76497cf45438aa2c","tid":1688660,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"點解好似冇咩人重視要制裁CCTVB<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實CCTVB做既野 係同狗,林病,律政司一樣仆街</span><br />\n基本上佢地不實報導係幫狗掩飾緊<br />\n唔好以為真係好多黃絲 <br />\n大撚把藍絲 只不過好多都冇出聲屌<br />\n基本上好多中年藍領同長者都係睇CCTVB<br />\n由一開始不實報導個時已經毒害左唔少人<br />\n一開始抗爭個時 如果CCTVB係正常報導<br />\n係會比到政府同狗唔少壓力 甚至係跪低<br />\n<br />\n唔理人權會唔會過到先 <br />\n但衝唔敢 驚比人拉<br />\n罷工唔敢 驚冇飯開<br />\n文宣唔敢 驚比人斬<br />\n咁唔該你同我簽咗佢<br />\n<br />\n1. 制裁TVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32jy4fj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32jy4fj&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=639bfce4\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32jy4fj</a><br />\n尚欠60000人聯署，11月9日截止。<br />\n2. 解散警隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31gWPHR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31gWPHR&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=45f68d03\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31gWPHR</a><br />\n尚欠 16000 人聯署，11 月 9日截止。<br />\n3.重組政府同HKPOPO<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/re-establish-government-and-hk-police\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fre-establish-government-and-hk-police&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=d093c153\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/re-establish-government-and-hk-police</a><br />\n<br />\n簽完幫我推 頂上去<br />\nP牌仔推到比人禁言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c3c29dad5187de249a84f315939c427b312007","tid":1688660,"uid":293667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i